726523f-a.title: Queens: Elderts Lane - Atlantic Avenue
726523f-a.text:
Elderts Lane, east side, between Atlantic Ave., and Jamaica Ave.
This house may have been also on the north side of New Lots Road, just
west of Elderts Lane. It is said to be the oldest Eldert house, being
erected in 1770. It is no longer standing.
1895.
Eumene L. Ambruster Collection.
